{{doomwiki}}[[Image:Reelism_01.png|thumb|300px|The Internet Machine]] {{Wad | name = Reelism | author = 300 Pounds (The Kinsie and The Shadsy) | iwad = Doom2 | type = m | status = Released | link = [http://thekinsie.com/reelism/ Official site] | caco = 19 }} '''Reelism''' is a tongue-in-cheek variation on the "invasion" gameplay. It offers large, wide-open maps in which random monsters and weapons will constantly spawn during themed rounds. The "reel" mechanism also provide other game-changing effects which can help or, usually, hinder the players. Everything is filled with homages to classic gaming, in-jokes, and all-around silliness.
The extreme randomness of the mod makes the gameplay rather unpredictable, since it is possible to obtain extremely unfair combinations as well as ridiculously easy ones.
